{"tid":392362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港搵d樣衰穿公仔衫，台灣公仔衫背後竟然係美女","createTime":"2017-09-08T12:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T14:11:31.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a46de969a36ebf339b6d60cef2a66ac5dfc40b35","tid":392362,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"2017台北世大運紅到海外超旺的吉祥物「熊讚」無人不知無人不曉，不過更特別的是，「熊讚」背後的操偶師之一為台北市教育局員工鄭可渼，由於外型出眾，網友看到後都大喊「戀愛惹」！<br />\n<br />\n平常大家看到的「熊讚」，其實背後有個堅強經紀團隊，甚至還有經紀人，負責安排所有活動演出，保母是負責現場引導，操偶師就是要穿著厚重的熊偶來扮演「熊讚」，總計成員20名，都是市府員工，要輪流做三種職務。<br />\n<br />\n特別的是，一般想到的操偶師都是要能夠耐的住高溫的壯漢，要能夠穿著厚重裝配唱唱跳跳，沒想到熊讚的「真面目」曝光，竟然是正妹一位，不僅讓網友讚嘆，也凸顯出擔任操偶師的辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，鄭可渼也參與設計世大運的周邊商品，像是徽章、台灣熊讚束口袋等，可以說多才多藝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/203033_ef5ccf3d40480c8de0862bd2f9501329.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F203033_ef5ccf3d40480c8de0862bd2f9501329.jpg&h=c29e76d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/203047_66ae196cf9ab9171380211922a92d32f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F203047_66ae196cf9ab9171380211922a92d32f.jpg&h=27b6b8a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣真係寶島"},{"pid":"b7994f6840ac480be44d1113c446fc5fcc98dca2","tid":392362,"uid":60785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"taiwan no.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38948515b959389da47cbf27bb08d9413e677e2","tid":392362,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:33:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54f4d9f9f1f295bb316cbb3f9c00ce0dd81aa02c","tid":392362,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"台灣女生，我最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012f62c4a2e0f03c577fa8a37dc6ebe84b02982b","tid":392362,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"里面索曬條女啲汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8058eda8d7ce8f46154c6c1b3143f66f2931d16","tid":392362,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:52:54.000Z","msg":"台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693a1072deafa9821c9868a875f4a915962a3792","tid":392362,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>里面索曬條女啲汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出晒汁之後就狂奶條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23ac927f8868906a01a56e6d77e93595795f0c6","tid":392362,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:09:38.000Z","msg":"操偶師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5ced259102e86ab4a50be18ba77c48f94c8457","tid":392362,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}